# ==========================================================
# Cohesity Backup Validation – SQL + Oracle + FS
# TARGETED PG INSPECTION VERSION
#
# GET ONLY | SEARCH ONLY | NO FULL INVENTORY
#
# Output:
# InputCI | BackupType | ObjectName | ClusterName | ProtectionGroup | LastBackupTime
#
# Logic:
# - DBNAME@SERVERNAME:
#     * Search DBNAME for SQL/Oracle.
#     * Search SERVERNAME for FS.
#     * Print only that DB and that server FS.
#
# - SERVERNAME:
#     * Search SERVERNAME for FS.
#     * Search SERVERNAME for SQL/Oracle candidate PGs.
#     * If candidate PG found, inspect only that PG and try to print DB names.
#
# - DBNAME:
#     * Search DBNAME for SQL/Oracle.
#     * If DB host is found from PG/run details, also try FS for that host.
#
# Important:
# - Does NOT scan all SQL/Oracle PGs across all clusters.
# - Does NOT scan all clusters if global search cannot find candidate cluster/PG.
# - Does targeted PG run inspection only for candidate PGs found by search.
# - DB names are best-effort from targeted SQL run objects / Oracle PG params.
# - Validation CSV is not generated.
# ==========================================================

